  CONTEXT: ~/.claude/skills/fixit/SKILL.md, .buildrunner/fixit-briefs/, .buildrunner/codex-allowed.flag
  WHY: Reflexion research shows gains concentrate in the first reflection; 2+ rounds cause oscillation not improvement. Explicit cap prevents infinite-loop failure modes.
  CONTEXT: /fixit Step 5 arbitration
